n june  view all reports and presentations share price view share price chart careers our people are highly motivated proud to work for us and highly evolved in the decision making process that is the crucial key to our success go to careers site map privacy disclaimer sign up for email alerts   altri altri  wikipedia altri from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search altri sgps sa type sociedade anónima traded as euronext altr industry paper and pulp energy founded  headquarters porto portugal key people paulo fernandes chairman  ceo products bleached wood pulp cogeneration biomass power plants revenue € million  operating income € million  profit € million  number of employees  website altript altri sgps sa is a portuguese industrial conglomerate headquartered in porto the groups main companies operate in wood pulp production cultivation of forests for the timber and paper industry and cogeneration of energy including energy production from renewable resources prior to  the group also operated in the steelworks industry altris holding company is altri sgps sa which is listed on the euronext lisbon stock exchange its major subsidiaries are celulose do caima paper industry and celbi paper industry altris f ramada subsidiary which produced steel and storage systems such as cold rolled steel sheets and strips machinery tools and other related products was spun off on the stock exchange in  altri was itself born from a spinout of the industrial assets of the cofina group in march  referencesedit  a b c annual report  altri retrieved  july    altri says new shares from steel unit spinoff to start trading early july afx news forbes  june  retrieved  november    lisbon shares sharply higher as bcp rockets  pct after it loses bcr deal afx news forbes  december  retrieved  november   external linksedit official website v t e psi companies of portugal altri banco comercial português banco português de investimento banif ctt correios de portugal energias de 